		&lt;tr style=&#34;color: #323752; background-color: #f2f7f7;&#34;&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
				&lt;ol&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;windows上安装。①安装erlang。 https://www.erlang.org/ ②下载rabbitmq-server-windows-x.xx.xx.zip https://www.rabbitmq.com/install-windows-manual.html③解压运行 rabbitmq-server.bat -detached(This will start a node in the background (not attached to the Command Prompt).)。&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;rabbitmqctl status查看RabbitMQ是否正常启动。&lt;/li&gt;
